<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <h1>여기는 게시글을 쓸 수 있는 부분입니다.</h1>
      <form action="/posts/create" method="post">
        <p style="font-weight: bold;">제목 :
          <input name="title" type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="제목을 입력하세요" style="width: 60%;">
        </p>
        <p style="font-weight: bold;">내용 :
           <textarea name="content" class="form-control" rows="3" placeholder="내용을 입력하세요" style="width: 60%;"></textarea>
        </p>
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-default">Submit</button>
      </form>
    <h1><a href="/">게시글 보러가기</a></h1>
  </div>
</div>
